public class History
extends AnnotationElement

Contains all the history information about a Model (or other SBase if level >= 3).

isEmpty

public boolean isEmpty()
Checks whether at least one attribute has been set for this History.

Returns:
true if at least one of the possible attributes is set, i.e., not null:
  • creation date
  • listOfCreators is not null and contains at least one element
  • listOfModification is not null and contains at least one element.
  • modified is not null.
